# Scratch + chunking is allocation-amortized: at the dominant 1024-pixel width
# the deltas are within noise. The previous behaviour (per-call Vec) is now a
# one-time grow on the first call, then zero allocation thereafter. Chunking
# also caps working-set memory regardless of input length — verified by
# pipeline_memory_bounded_by_chunk_size in tests/simd_parity.rs (chunk=64
# stayed at 64-pixel capacity processing a 10000-pixel strip).
